data.description: Built in 2012, this immaculate residence offers a spacious and comfortable living space spanning over 2,654 square feet. Boasting exceptional craftsmanship and thoughtful design, this home is sure to impress even the most discerning buyers.    Step inside and be greeted by the inviting ambiance of the open-concept layout. The first floor features stunning hardwood flooring throughout, creating a seamless flow between the living areas. The heart of the home is the expansive kitchen, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining guests. With its ample counter space, built-in cabinetry, and a large kitchen island capable of accommodating up to 10 people, this kitchen is a true centerpiece.    On the upper level, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, including a massive master suite that exudes luxury. Relax and unwind in the master bathroom, complete with a soaking tub, standing shower, and a convenient walk-in closet. The second floor also offers a convenient laundry area with cabinets and a sink, ensuring effortless daily routines.    Outside, the large backyard is an oasis awaiting your personal touch. With tasteful landscaping, there is plenty of space for outdoor activities and potential for creating your dream outdoor retreat.    Additional features of this remarkable property include carpeted living areas upstairs, providing comfort and warmth, and the added benefit of owned solar panels, reducing your energy costs and environmental footprint.    Located in North Hanford, this home offers a peaceful neighborhood setting while still being close to amenities, schools, and shopping centers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own.
